    <div class="card w-100 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">History and Geography</h2>
            <p>
                America, also known as the United States of America, has a rich
                history that dates back to the arrival of Native Americans thousands
                of years ago. It became a country on July 4, 1776, with the
                Declaration of Independence. The USA is located in North America,
                bordered by Canada to the north, Mexico to the south, the Atlantic
                Ocean to the east, and the Pacific Ocean to the west.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

